------------
FLIGHT
------------
        name: check.valid.search

            1. Open Flight form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Fill out "from" and "to" fields
            4. click Search

            Expected: New history record contains entered dates and "from"-"to" values
        ------------
        name: check.remove.record

            1. Open Flight form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Fill out "from" and "to" fields
            4. click Search
            5. click Remove button in 'Previous searches' block

            expected result: result was removed from Previous searches
        ------------
        name: check.clear.form

            1. Open Flight form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Fill out "from" and "to" fields
            4. click Clear button

            expected result: form was cleared: start and end dates are set to default, 'From' and 'To' are empty
        ------------
        name: check.empty.search

            1. Open Flight form
            2. Clear dates fields
            3. click search

            expected result: validation message appeared
        ------------
        name: check.location.dropdown.menu

            1. Open Flight form
            2. Type any valid values in 'From' and 'To'

            expected result: Should be displayed drop-down menu with 'From' and 'To' locations
------------
CARS
------------
        name: check.valid.search

            1. Open Cars form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Amenities" value
            4. Enter any "Location"
            5. click Search

            Expected: New record contains entered dates, "Amenities" and "Location" values
        ------------
        name: check.remove.record

            1. Open Cars form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Type" value
            4. Enter any "Location"
            5. click Search
            6. click remove button

            expected result: result was removed from Previous searches
        ------------
        name: check.clear.form

            1. Open Cars form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Type" value
            4. Enter any "Location"
            5. click Clear button

            expected result: form was cleared
        ------------
        name: check.empty.search

            1. Open Cars form
            2. Clear dates fields
            3. Click Search

            expected result: new record should not be added to the Previous searches
        ------------
        name: check.location.dropdown.menu

            1. Open Cars form
            2. Type any valid value to 'Location'

            expected result: Should be displayed drop-down menu with available locations
------------
HOTELS
------------
        name: check.valid.search

            1. Open Hotels form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Amenities" value
            4. Enter any valid "Location"
            5. click Search

            Expected: New record contains entered dates, stars amount and "Location" values
        ------------
        name: check.remove.record

            1. Open Hotels form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Amenities" value
            4. Enter any "Location"
            5. click Search
            6. click remove button

            expected result: result was removed from Previous searches
        ------------
        name: check.clear.form

            1. Open Hotels form
            2. Pick any valid dates
            3. Select any "Amenities" value
            4. Enter any "Location"
            5. click Clear button

            expected result: form was cleared - start, end dates and 'Amenities' are set to default, 'Location' is empty
        ------------
        name: check.empty.search

            1. Open Hotels form
            2. Clear dates fields
            3. click search

            expected result: new record should not be added to the Previous searches
        ------------